QUICK FAQ

Q: Can I use this Firebase adapter in my commercial application?
A: Yes! Use it freely in your web apps, APIs, internal tools, etc.

Q: Can I create extensions for this Firebase adapter?
A: Yes, but you must include attribution and cannot sell them as products.

Q: Do I need to mention this adapter in my app's credits?
A: No, only if you create migration tools/extensions based on this adapter.

Q: Can I fork this adapter and improve it?
A: Yes, but keep the attribution and cannot sell it.

Q: Can my company use this Firebase adapter internally?
A: Absolutely! Internal use has no restrictions.

